intro: Help the dwarves carve out a new city!
description:
For centuries, the dwarves lived in peace and harmony, but dark magic has driven them from their ancestral lands. 
Help the dwarves build a new city where they can be safe from the threats of the past!

- Four types of gameplay to collect different resource types!
- Build a new town for Dwarves!
- beautiful and relaxing soundtrack!
